{"tid":41371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"死亡筆記，照亮新世紀","createTime":"2016-12-16T00:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T04:00:00.000Z","uid":11856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9aee6dfe2e4bc8e33ba4007be9a5ba5b17ae0b11","tid":41371,"uid":11856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T00:19:08.000Z","msg":"本身係死亡筆記忠實粉絲，<br />\n漫畫，動畫都有睇，<br />\n兩人鬥智鬥力，無論點都要見對方真身，<br />\n殺死對方，確實自己才是真正正義，<br />\n<br />\n昨晚，就狗衝去睇新死亡筆記，<br />\n睇到中段都悶，心諗繼承L真心廢定扮廢，還是又係假扮，仲有真正嘅L繼承嘅繼承者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就唔講劇情了，真心唔好睇，<br />\n唔好浪費兩粒鐘時間了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e212c8ca6dc2b4b15e4f4b64ace7879bb967b3","tid":41371,"uid":12442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T01:47:53.000Z","msg":"睇到一半想走"},{"pid":"59b46ad03ae9a3ec9cf3e2a32b13403f7cd46aa5","tid":41371,"uid":16187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T01:50:32.000Z","msg":"仲有伏筆先夠膽死"},{"pid":"cfedb67f780cf3a5b1d46a83d866326d870e8d17","tid":41371,"uid":11856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T04:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔明點解要六本筆記咁多"}]}